{
  "text": "Expressing T \u03b7 8 (0, 0) and T \u03b7 0 (0, 0) through the \u03b3\u03b3-decay constantsf \u03b7 8 (33) andf \u03b7 0 (34), we arrive at the standard (see, e.g. [CITATION_1] ) formulas for the \u03b7 and \u03b7 \u2032 decay widths:",
